      "options": {
        "mode": "markdown",
        "content": "## Agora \u2014 paper trading\n**Virtual money only** (eToro demo, write-locked to demo by schema + credentials). Every bet is a committed prediction, graded mechanically at its horizon. The index line is the bar to beat \u2014 amounts in $ (1.234,56). Updates nightly at 22:37."
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "\ud83c\udfc1 The race \u2014 Agora NAV vs the index  ($)",
      "datasource": {
        "type": "mysql",
        "uid": "finops-ledger"
      },
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 8,
        "w": 16,
        "x": 0,
        "y": 3
      },
      "description": "Benchmark: VWRD.L (USD class of the VWRL all-world fund), normalized to the same start. Distributing class understates the index by ~2%/yr of dividends \u2014 a bias IN THE AGENT'S FAVOR until the total-return adjustment lands.",
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "locale",
          "decimals": 0,
          "custom": {
            "drawStyle": "line",
            "lineWidth": 2,
            "fillOpacity": 6,
            "showPoints": "auto",
            "pointSize": 5
          }
        },
        "overrides": [
